Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理被黑暗吞噬之前  童年由听觉  嗅觉和视觉主宰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:01:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片名:  穿条纹睡衣的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快走  -快走\N- move! - move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快!\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快!\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上车!\NNow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到家了\NIt's me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再见  布鲁诺  -再见  布鲁诺\N- Bye, Bruno! - bye, Bruno!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嘿  小甜心  -妈妈  这是在干什么\N- Hello, sweetheart. - mum, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们在庆祝  -庆祝?\N- We're celebrating. - celebrating?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸得到晋升了\NYour father's been given a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是一份更好的工作  我知道晋升的意思\NThat means a better job.  I know what promotion is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要开个小型聚会来庆祝一下\NSo we're having a little party to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他还是军人  对吧\NHe's still going to be a soldier though, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我的小羊羔  只是职务更重要了\NYes, my lamb. yes, just a more important one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有更令人振奋的消息呢\NThere's some even more exciting news,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸想亲口告诉你们\NBut I think dad wanted to tell you about that himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-搬家?  搬到哪里  -搬到乡下\N- Moving? where to? - to the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那离这儿很远的  卡尔  里奥和马丁怎么办\NThat's miles away. what about Karl and Leon and Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小甜心  我知道这并不容易\NSweetheart, I know it's hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们都必须\NBut we're all having to say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友暂时分别了\NTo our friends for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  我们还会交到新朋友  对吧\NAnyway, we'll make new ones where we're going. won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯当然  你会交到很多新朋友的\NOf course you are. you'll make lots of new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  你明早走之前\NBruno, you can have your friends around
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把朋友叫来玩\NIn the morning before we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它当作一次冒险  就像书上看到的\NThink of it as an adventure, like in one of your books.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这栋房子是最好的\NBut this is the best house ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不一定\NWell, you never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新房子也许会更好\NThe house we're going to might be even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸说那里有个花园\NDad says it's got a garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  布鲁诺  作为一名军人\NLook, the thing is, Bruno, the thing about being a soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活中没有很多选择  更多的是责任\NIs that life is not so much about choice, it's more about duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果国家需要你去  你就得去\NSo if your country needs you to go somewhere, you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  如果得到家人的支持\NNow, of course, going somewhere else is much easier
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家会更加开心\NWhen you know that your family are so delighted to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  每次见你都发现你长高了\NBruno! you're getting bigger every time I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莎尼  你才一个礼拜没见他\NIt's only been a week, Nathalie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是我变矮了吧\NWell, perhaps it's me that's getting smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩\NSo, you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是怎么想的  关于搬去柏林的事?\NWell, what do you think of all this? moving out of berlin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈说这是件好事\NWell, mummy and daddy say it's a good thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那准错不了\NSo I suppose it must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们  要乖乖的   去拿点吃的\NChildren, be angels, will you? pass some food around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希特勒万岁!\NHeil hitler!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺你\NCongratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他是不是很英俊  -绝对是\N- Doesn't he look wonderful? - absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真为你骄傲  我的孩子\NI'm so proud of you, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的  有时想起来想做梦\NOh, dear. I sometimes wonder if this is all down to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为小小的你\NMaking you those costumes for your little plays
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做话剧戏服\NWhen you were tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你那时喜爱盛装出场  -娜莎尼\N- You used to adore all that dressing up. - Nathalie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在仍让你觉得与众不同么  亲爱的拉尔夫\NDoes it still make you feel special, Ralf dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身制服和它的含义\NThe uniform and what it stands for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲  这是次聚会  我们不要破坏气氛\NMother, it's a party. let's not spoil things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  破坏气氛?\NMe, spoil things?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该小心\NYou should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此公然发表意见可能会给你带来麻烦\NAiring your views so publicly could land you in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是知道的\NYou know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得有多长时间不能见你  我的孩子\NSo, how long are we losing you for, my boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我想是到战争胜利之时  -那不会很久的\N- Until the war is won, I would think. - well, not so long then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺\NBruno!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  该说再见了\NAll right, Bruno. time to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再见  -再见\N- Bye-bye. - bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主  入睡时分以至  感谢你的守护\NTime has come for me to sleep lord, I thank thee for thy keep
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚美妙的夜色  教导我要信赖你\NWatch this night well over me and teach me, lord, to trust in thee
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关爱幼小  生病  贫穷的人们\NCare for children, sick and poor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施恩于他们的人  主  你会给予更多祝福\NGrant them, lord, thy blessing more
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以基督的名义祈祷  同样关爱我的家人\NAnd this I pray in jesus' name care for my family just the same"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿门\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们  看  快看  我们的新家\NChildren, look. look! our new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些事要处理  一会儿见\NI have some business to take care of. I'll see you shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得怎么样\NWell, what do we think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  不是很好么\NCome on. it's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩去选房间吧  我去把玛利亚叫来\NYou two choose your rooms. I'll have Maria come
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她帮你们拿行李\NAnd help you unpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我们的新房子怎么样  玛利亚\NWhat do you think of it, Maria? the new house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不该我来说\NIt's not for me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好摆设一下才有家的感觉  对吧\NBut it won't feel like home until we make it feel like home, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他准备好了么\NIs he already up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是谁\NWho was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸的士兵  我猜\NOne of your father's soldiers, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:14:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他看上去很严肃  -他们都很严肃  对吧\N- He looked very serious. - well, they are, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们为什么要小声说话  -我不知道\N- Why are we whispering? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-和谁一起玩  -农场上的小孩\N- And play with who? - the children over on the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,农场?  我没看到过呀  把那个也递过来\NFarm? I didn't see a farm. and that one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我的房间能看到\NYou can only see it from my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有小孩子?\NAnd there are some children there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-对  有很多  -那太好了\N- Yes, quite a few. - that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那我能和他们一起玩吧  -当然可以\N- So, I'll be able to play with them. - I don't see why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先等等  看看他们怎么样\NI'll wait a little bit, just to see what they're like,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-因为他们看上去有点怪  -那些孩子么\N- Because they look a bit strange. - the children do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-对  还有农民  -怎么个怪法\N- Well, and the farmers. - what sort of strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蔬菜\NVegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放那儿\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  你的东西都放好了么\NBruno, have you unpacked everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你该回楼上去把活干完\NBecause I think you should go back upstairs and finish off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您  太太\NThank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺\NBruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我说过了他们很怪  -谁\N- I told you they were strange. - who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些农民  他们穿着睡衣\NThe farmers. they wear pyjamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  我正找你呢\NBruno, I was just coming to look for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的帮助  那很管用\NWell, thank you for that. that was extremely useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-待会儿见  -是  指挥官\N- I'll be over to see you later. - of course, Herr Kommandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来\NCome in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下  坐下\NSit down, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎么样\NWell, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\NOh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回家\NI want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是家  布鲁诺  家就是家人所在的地方\NYou are home, Bruno. home is where the family is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对么\NIsn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺   你至少试着适应这里\NBruno, you have to at least give the place a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保证  用不了多久你就\NI promise you, it won't be long before you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么农民都穿着睡衣\NWhy do the farmers wear pyjamas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能从窗户看到他们\NI can see them from my window.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  事实上  那些人\NThe thing is, Bruno, those people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们根本不算人\NWell, you see, they're not really people at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  谁告诉你那里是个农场\NBruno, who told you it was a farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是玛利亚吗  -不是\N- Was it Maria? - no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里就是个农场  对么\NIt is a farm, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里与你的新工作有关么\NIs it to do with your new job?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  你只需知道我在这里的工作\NAll you need to know about my work here, Bruno,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们的国家和你都很重要\NIs that it's very important to our country and to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在非常努力的工作\NWe're working very hard to make this world a better place
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让你在更好的世界中成长\NFor you to grow up in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不是个农民  你是个军人\NBut you're not a farmer. you're a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  能过来帮我\NBruno, can you come and help me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整理一下厨房么\NFinish sorting out in the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是可以和那些孩子一起玩  对么\NI can still play with them, though? the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  看来不行了\NI don't think so, Bruno. no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你说的  他们有点怪  有点儿...\NLike you say, they're a bit strange. a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们和你不一样\NWell, they're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  宝贝  我们会交到新朋友的\NDon't worry, my darling. we'll find you some new friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是农场上的那些人\NBut they won't be the ones from the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉尔夫  你向我保证过\NRalf, you promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你说农场离这儿很远  -没错\N- you said it was miles away. - it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能知道他能从卧室的窗户看到它\NHow was I to know he could see it from the bedroom window?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们中的一员就在我们的厨房\NThere was one of them in our kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-布鲁诺小主人  今天过的怎么样  -很烦\N- Master Bruno, how are you today? - fed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这两周每天都说同样的话\NYou said the same thing every day for two whole weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-没错  -你应该到外面去玩\N- It's true. - well, you should be out playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-和谁  -不知道  格雷特尔怎么样\N- Playing with who? - I don't know. Gretel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你可以自娱自乐  -我正在努力那么做\N- Well, you can make your own fun. - that's what I'm trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我很肯定\NOne thing's for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦地坐在这里不会让你更快乐\NSitting around being miserable won't make things any happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-布鲁诺  你在干什么  -探险\N- Bruno, what are you doing? - exploring!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不  不许去后面  我说过那里禁止入内\NNo! no, not in the back. I told you, it's out of bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-回前面去探险  -但我已经探遍那里了\N- Explore at the front. - but I've explored it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那就找点别的事干  -比如什么呢\N- Well, find something else to do. - like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回屋  我们想想干些什么\NCome back in now, and we'll think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:21:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们  今天做了什么\NSo, children, what are you doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-和昨天一样  -昨天你干什么了\N- Same as yesterday. - and what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-和前天一样  -除了去探险\N- Same as the day before. - except you went exploring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我喜欢探险  -你去哪儿了\N- I like exploring. - where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到后花园去看看  但妈妈不让\NI wanted to look in the back garden, but mum wouldn't let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后花园?\NThe back garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别去\NWell, god forbid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想念你的那些朋友了吧\NI expect you'll be missing those friends of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至想念学校\NI even miss school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢想象你会这么说\NWell, I never thought I'd hear you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  你不会想念很久的\NAnyway, you won't be missing it for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真的?  -我给你们两个找了个家庭教师\N- Really? - I've arranged a tutor for you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李斯特先生每周会来两次\NA herr Liszt will be visiting twice a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不去学校?\NSo we're not going to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.51,0:21:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校会来这里?\NSchool's coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.52,0:21:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑着我弄到的旧自行车来这里\NOn an old bicycle, I gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一只失去你的小鸟\NIt's a bird without you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小家伙  今天早上怎么样\NGood morning, little man. and how are you this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-能问你点事么  -问吧\N- Can I ask you a favour? - well, you can ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近有多余的轮胎么\NAre there any spare tyres around?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.87,0:22:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如卡车上的旧轮胎什么的\NAn old one from one of the trucks or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.41,0:22:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这附近我看到的唯一的旧轮胎\NWell, the only spare tyre I've seen around here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于麦博格上尉\NBelongs to Lieutenant Meinberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他还在用它么  -是的  他很需要那东西\N- Well, is he using it? - yes, he's very attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.89,0:23:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了  他不懂  他才八岁\NStop it. he doesn't understand. he's only eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.72,0:23:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才十二岁  别假装你多大似的\NYou're only 12, so stop pretending you're any older.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想要轮胎干什么\NWhat do you want a tyre for, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做个秋千  -秋千?\N- I want to make a swing. - a swing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来挺棒的\NThat does sound exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.74,0:23:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你!\NYou!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上过来\NHere, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快!\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带这个孩子到后花园的外屋\NTake this boy to the outhouse in the back garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那儿有很多轮胎  让他挑一个\NThere are some tyres in there. he will select one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后带上他挑的轮胎  明白么\NYou will carry it where he asks. do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.26,0:23:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小家伙  还等什么呢\NWell, little man, what are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.85,0:24:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样\NHow about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.07,0:25:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈在哪儿\NWhere's my mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.66,0:25:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她出去了\NShe's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.78,0:25:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她什么时候回来  -很快  我猜\N- When is she back? - soon, I expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.58,0:25:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心\NBut don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.08,0:25:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但我可能会因失血而亡的  -不  你不会\N- But I might bleed to death. - no, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.55,0:25:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我需要去医院么  不  这只是个小伤口\N- Will I need to go to hospital? - no. it's only a small cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.56,0:25:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  没那么痛\NCome on. it's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.60,0:25:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  没事了\NThere, all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.20,0:26:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你叫什么  -帕维尔\N- What's your name? - Pavel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.62,0:26:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你出去玩儿之前\NNow, you've got to sit still for a few minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.21,0:26:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还得在这儿坐几分钟\NBefore you start walking around on that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.96,0:26:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会把这事告诉我妈妈么\NWill you tell my mum what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.59,0:26:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她会自己发现的\NI think she's going to see it for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.47,0:26:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她大概会带我去看医生的\NShe'll probably take me to a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.35,0:26:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不会\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.19,0:26:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这伤可能比看起来更糟糕  -不会的\N- It could be worse than it looks. - it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.48,0:26:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道  你又不是医生\NHow would you know? you're not a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.78,0:26:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我是  -不  你不是\N- Yes, I am. - no, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.95,0:26:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是削土豆的\NYou peel potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.04,0:26:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受过医生训练\NI practised as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.29,0:26:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我...\NBefore i...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.92,0:27:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我来这里之前\NBefore I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.21,0:27:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要接受训练  你的医术一定不高\NYou couldn't have been much good then, if you had to practise.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.64,0:27:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你长大后想当什么呢\NNow, what are you going to be when you grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.31,0:27:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  一个探险家\NI know. an explorer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.19,0:27:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的\NHow do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.28,0:27:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在农场上好么\NIs it nice on the farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.08,0:27:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  你这是怎么回事\NBruno. Bruno, what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.79,0:27:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了个秋千\NI made a swing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.67,0:27:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我从上面掉了下来还摔伤了膝盖\Nbut I fell off it and cut my knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.63,0:27:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕维尔把我抱了进来  还为我缠了绷带\NBut Pavel here, he carried me in and put a bandage on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.47,0:28:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-回你的房间去  -但帕维尔说我得...\N- Go to your room. - but Pavel says i...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.48,0:28:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别顶嘴  回房间去\NDon't argue. go to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.88,0:28:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.66,0:28:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这儿有如此的景色  这真不公平\NIt's not fair, you having this view.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.37,0:29:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不跟你换屋\NWell, I'm not swapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.38,0:29:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是学校来了\NI think school's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.05,0:29:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是说更近代的历史\NNo, I mean more recent history.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.38,0:29:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你对时事新闻感兴趣么  -是的  非常感兴趣\N- Are you interested in current affairs? - yes, very.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.22,0:29:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你即将知道\NSo, you'll be aware of the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.06,0:29:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们伟大的民族所处的局势\NIn which our great nation presently finds itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.52,0:29:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我一有空就去读报  而且父亲的一个士兵\NYes. I read newspapers whenever I can and one of father's men
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.94,0:29:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总能让我了解最新时事\NKeeps me up to date on everything that's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.02,0:29:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  还有你布鲁诺  你看报纸么\NGood. and you, Bruno. have you been reading newspapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.40,0:29:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那你看什么读物吗  -书\N- Have you been reading anything? - books.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.83,0:29:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  什么类型的书\NGood. what sort of books?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.29,0:29:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是冒险类图书\NAdventure books, mainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.25,0:29:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道  例如穿着银盔亮甲的骑士\NYou know, knights in shining armour
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.79,0:29:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在探索陌生的土地和物品\NExploring strange lands and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.05,0:29:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有愚蠢的公主们总是碍手碍脚的\NAnd silly princesses always getting in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.51,0:29:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我来帮忙的原因\NWell, this is why I'm here to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.72,0:29:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在多大了  布鲁诺  八岁吧\Nyou're how old now, Bruno? eight?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.80,0:30:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候让你忘掉那些科幻书籍了\NTime to get your head out of those fiction books
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.76,0:30:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且开始学习真相\NAnd start learning about fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.93,0:30:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想该到让你面对真实世界的时候了\NTime, I think, to turn your mind to the real world,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.69,0:30:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信这本书会是个完美的开端\NAnd I believe this would be the perfect start.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.70,0:31:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧  死吧!\NDie, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.17,0:32:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧  死吧!\NDie, die.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.98,0:32:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.19,0:33:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在探险\NI'm exploring.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.45,0:33:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你在干什么  -我们...  我们正在修建一个新棚屋\N- What are you doing? - we're... we're building a new hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.17,0:33:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边很多都是你的朋友么\NHave you got lots of friends over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.84,0:33:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些是  但我们总是打架\NA few. but we fight a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.05,0:33:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我坐在这里  可以自己一个人待着\NThat's why I like being out here. I can be on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.18,0:33:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我叫布鲁诺  -我叫沙暮\N- I'm Bruno. - Shmuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.48,0:33:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -我叫沙暮\N- sorry? - I'm Shmuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.15,0:33:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的名字?  从没听过这样的名字\NThat's your name? never heard of anyone called that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.07,0:33:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也从没听过有人叫布鲁诺\NI've never heard of anyone called bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.36,0:33:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙暮  谁会叫沙暮啊\NBut Shmuel. no one's called Shmuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.21,0:33:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家在那后面\NI live in the house, back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.71,0:34:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你身上有吃的吗  -没有\N- Have you got any food on you? - no.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.97,0:34:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你饿了?\NAre you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.73,0:34:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你几岁\NHow old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.10,0:34:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-8岁  -我也是呢!\N- Eight. - me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.74,0:34:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不公平  我整天被关在家里自己待着\NIt's not fair, me being stuck over here on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.49,0:34:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你却能整天和朋友们玩游戏\NWhile you're over there, playing with friends all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.37,0:34:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-游戏？  -那号码\N- Playing? - well, that number.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.62,0:34:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-游戏不是要排号吗  -只是我的编号\N- Isn't it a part of a game or something? - it's just my number.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.13,0:34:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有不同的编号\NEveryone gets given a different number.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.80,0:34:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  然后怎么玩?\NRight. then what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.05,0:34:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我得回去了!  -真的?\N- I have to go back now! - really?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.72,0:34:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.26,0:34:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙暮  见到你真好\NIt was nice to meet you, Shmuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.48,0:34:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  布鲁诺\NAnd you, Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.32,0:35:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.42,0:35:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  我的足球不见了\NMum, I can't find my football.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.54,0:35:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝  去柜厨里找找\NWell, it'll be in one of your cupboards, sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.84,0:35:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  我找过了\NIt isn't. I've looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.38,0:35:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以吃条巧克力吗\NCan I have a piece of chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.43,0:35:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一条  可以\NA piece. yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.81,0:35:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺\NBruno?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.69,0:35:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-找地下室了吗  -地下室?\N- have you looked in the cellar? - the cellar?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.86,0:35:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你的球\NFor your football.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.86,0:36:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死\NDamn.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.09,0:36:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-格雷特尔  我看见你所有的...-我的什么\N- Gretel, I've just seen all your... - all my what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.68,0:37:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的洋娃娃  在地下室\NAll your dolls, down in the cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.73,0:37:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女孩才要洋娃娃\NDolls are for little girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.06,0:37:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不该只顾着玩傻娃娃\NIt's not right to play with silly toys
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.86,0:37:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人人都在为咱们国家无私奉献呢\NWhile people are away risking their lives for the fatherland.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.49,0:37:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-"吾族之命论乃吾之命论"  -是"命运"\N- "My people's density is my density." - destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.03,0:38:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"吾欲与吾族同舟共济  荣辱与共"\N"lts struggles and its sorrows, its joys and its miseries are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.83,0:38:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"吾欲为吾国之复兴鞠躬尽瘁  死而后己"\N"i must work and create for the resurrection of my fatherland.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.54,0:38:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"吾族上下皆荣耀英勇之士"\N"the history of my people is great and glorious."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.21,0:38:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12点了\NAnd it's 12:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.80,0:38:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉  接着读   -不是该下课了吗\N- I'm sorry? - isn't that when we finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.01,0:38:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  什么时候下课老师说了算\NThe termination of the lesson is for the tutor to decide, Bruno,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.27,0:38:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生说了不算  请你继续\NNot the pupil. now, will you please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.41,0:38:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  你跑哪去了\NBruno, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.87,0:38:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要进城办点事  想一起来吗\NI'm just going into town for an hour. do you want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.88,0:38:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荡秋千一定要小心\NYou be careful on that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.42,0:38:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.90,0:39:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你个问题\NCan I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.19,0:39:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为啥整天都穿睡衣\NWhy do you people wear pyjamas all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.57,0:39:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-它们不是睡衣  -看起来好像\N- They're not pyjamas. - well, those.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.78,0:39:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没别的穿的  他们把我们衣服拿走了\NWe have to. they took all our other clothes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.91,0:39:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谁拿走的  -当兵的\N- Who did? - the soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.83,0:39:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些军人  为什么\NThe soldiers? why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.50,0:39:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢那些当兵的  你呢\NI don't like soldiers. do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.17,0:39:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜欢  我爸爸就是个军人\NI do, quite. my dad's a soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.97,0:39:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定不会\NBut not the sort
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.51,0:39:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无缘无故拿走别人衣服\Nthat takes people's clothes away for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.34,0:39:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪种呢\NWhat sort, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.76,0:39:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是当大官儿的\NWell, he's the important sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.56,0:39:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸能让大家都过的好\NHe's in charge of making everything better for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.06,0:39:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那你爸爸是农民吗  -不  他是修表的\N- So is your dad a farmer? - no, he's a watchmaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.57,0:40:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来修表  现在大多数时间他在修鞋\NOr was. most of the time now, he just mends boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.74,0:40:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些大人脑子真是坏掉了\NIt's funny how grown-ups can't make their minds up
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.00,0:40:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道自己想干什么  就像帕维尔\NAbout what they want to do. it's like Pavel.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.17,0:40:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识他吗  他住那里\NDo you know him? lives over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.09,0:40:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以前是个医生  现在却在削土豆皮\NHe used to be a doctor, but gave it all up to peel potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.43,0:40:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再问你个问题\NCan I ask you another question?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.31,0:40:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们烟筒里面烧的什么呀\NWhat do you burn in those chimneys?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.73,0:40:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有天看见冒烟了  是些干草什么的吗\NI saw them going the other day. is it just lots of hay and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.48,0:40:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  我们不能到那儿去\NI don't know. we're not allowed over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.61,0:40:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说是些旧衣服\NMama says it's old clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.91,0:40:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么  真难闻\NWell, whatever it is, it smells horrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.95,0:40:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想你带块巧克力来\NI wish you'd remembered the chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.21,0:40:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\NYes, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.92,0:40:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到了  你可以哪天来我家吃饭\NI know! Perhaps you can come and have supper with us sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.96,0:40:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能  因为这个\NI can't, can i? because of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.30,0:41:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是不让动物出去的呀\NBut that's to stop the animals getting out, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.88,0:41:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动物  不  是不让人出去的\NAnimals? no, it's to stop people getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.64,0:41:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能出来吗\NAre you not allowed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.60,0:41:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-为什么  你做错什么了  -我是犹太人\N- Why? what have you done? - I'm a Jew.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.32,0:41:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我该走了\NI think I should go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.29,0:41:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你明天还来这么  -我试试看\N- Will you be here tomorrow? - I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.87,0:41:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好的  拜拜  -拜\N- Goodbye, then! - bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.01,0:41:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝  给你小礼物\NLittle present, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.68,0:41:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  妈妈\NThank you, mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.27,0:42:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-瞧见布鲁诺没  -外面玩秋千呢吧\N- Have you seen Bruno? - outside on his swing, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.29,0:42:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行  周四正好  我派辆车接你俩\NYes, thursday's perfect. I'll have a car come to collect you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.04,0:42:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷奶奶要来吗\NAre grandma and grandpa coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.71,0:42:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那天闻到那股臭味儿了吗\NHey, did you smell that horrible smell the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.01,0:42:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-烟囱里飘出来的臭烟味儿  -哪种病\N- Coming from the chimneys. - what sort of ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.72,0:42:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从秋千上掉下来那天\NThe day I fell off the swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.60,0:42:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-妈妈  你闻到了吗  -爸\N- Did you smell it, mum? - father.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.43,0:42:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\NMum.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.60,0:42:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我跟她说\NLet me speak to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.40,0:42:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我能听见她\NYes, she is. I can hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.90,0:42:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我们也盼着呢  再见\NYes. we look forward to it. goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.12,0:42:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-奶奶不来了吗  -是的\N- Is grandma not coming? - no.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.75,0:43:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎她身体很不好  不过爷爷要来\NShe's poorly, apparently, but grandpa's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.42,0:43:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你闻到了吗  爸爸  -闻什么\N- Did you smell it, dad? - what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.63,0:43:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟囱飘出来的臭味儿  是什么\NThat horrid smell from the chimneys. what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.89,0:43:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想有时他们烧垃圾吧\NI think they just burn rubbish there sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.27,0:43:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那儿  -哪儿\N- Look. - what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.98,0:43:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-噢!  -格雷特尔\N- Hey! - Gretel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.52,0:43:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不公平!\NHey, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.11,0:43:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-格雷特尔  -什么\N- Gretel. - what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.19,0:43:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个游戏\NIt's only a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.20,0:43:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉尔夫  你请的这个家教老师\NRalf, this tutor you brought in,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.79,0:43:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他教的孩子像格雷特尔和布鲁诺这么大的吗\NDoes he usually teach children as young as Gretel and Bruno?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.17,0:43:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是吧  怎么啦\NI believe so. why?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.88,0:43:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是不是该了解一下他的教学内容\NWell, do we know what he's teaching them?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.88,0:43:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷特尔似乎变得有点\NGretel seems to have become so...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.80,0:43:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们学的\NThey're being taught
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.84,0:43:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和现在孩子们学的一样\NWhat all children are being taught at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.42,0:43:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不能掉队\NThey mustn't get left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.59,0:43:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想了\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.81,0:43:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们休息吧\NLet's get to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.15,0:44:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"犹太之流诟吾族  诱吾族之敌"\N"The jew slandered us and incited our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.95,0:44:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"犹太之流以恶书腐吾族"\N"The jew corrupted us through bad books.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.41,0:44:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"其笑吾族文学音律"\N"He mocked our literature and our music.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.83,0:44:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"凡其所到之处 灾害不断"\N"Everywhere, his influence was destructive,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.25,0:44:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"吾国必因其而亡  不远矣"\N"The eventual result of which was our nation's collapse,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.25,0:44:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-"然..."  -什么事  布鲁诺\N- "And then..." - yes, Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.58,0:44:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.92,0:44:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一个人就能让一个国家沦亡\NA nation's collapse is all down to this one man?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.01,0:44:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"其"这里指的是"整个犹太民族"\NThe Jew here means the entire jewish race.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.59,0:44:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果单指一个人的话\NIf it had been just one man,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.64,0:44:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真应该千刀万剐了他\NI'm sure something would've been done about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.35,0:44:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是犹太人里面也有好人吧\NThere is such a thing as a nice Jew, though, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.60,0:44:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  你要是遇到了一个好的犹太人\NI think, Bruno, if you ever found a nice jew,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.52,0:44:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你真是发现新大陆了\NYou would be the best explorer in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.78,0:44:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着读  格雷特尔\NContinue, Gretel.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.37,0:45:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"其野心乃统辖万民"\N"The aim of the jew is to become the ruler of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.54,0:45:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"欲开天辟地  然万物因之磨难重重"\N"The jew is not creative, but destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.21,0:45:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"其乃文化之敌"\N"He is the enemy of culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.79,0:45:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"数千吾族因其贫困潦倒"\N"Thousands of germans have been made poor by the Jew."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.48,0:45:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺小主人\NMaster Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.94,0:45:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么  你不是刚吃过午饭吗\NWhat are you doing? you've just had your lunch, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.65,0:45:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出去走走  但我怕饿\NI was going for a walk, and I thought I might get peckish.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.57,0:45:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别弄乱了书包  拿这儿来\NBut don't make a mess of your satchel. bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.45,0:45:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我帮你整理好  -不要  你别管\N- I'll wrap it properly for you. - no. it's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.04,0:45:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  是什么\NBruno, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.62,0:45:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿书包做什么\NWhat are you doing with your satchel?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.12,0:45:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李斯特老师给了我几本书  我想坐秋千上读\NHerr Liszt gave us some books. I'm going out on the swing to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.26,0:45:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-让我检查一下  -什么\N- Let me see. - what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.42,0:45:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-书啊  -不行\N- The books. - no.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.18,0:46:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  我只想知道李斯特老师让你看什么书\NBruno, I just want to see what books Herr Liszt has given you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.35,0:46:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我说谎了  -什么\N- I told a lie. - what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.60,0:46:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带的是...\NI've just got
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.73,0:46:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历险故事书\NAdventure books.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.66,0:46:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖  去吧\NGo on. off you go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.58,0:46:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚  晚饭多准备两个人的份\NNow, Maria, there's two extra for supper tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.96,0:46:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我公公要来\NThe kommandant's father will be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.21,0:46:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想科勒特上尉也会一起来\NAnd I believe Lieutenant Kotler is joining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.40,0:46:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.00,0:47:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦\NWhat's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.21,0:47:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-别扔过来  -为什么\N- Don't throw it back. - what? why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.63,0:47:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-很危险  -危险?\N- It's dangerous. - dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.80,0:47:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个球  来嘛\NIt's just a ball. come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.47,0:47:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爱玩吗\NDo you not like playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.94,0:47:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但不爱玩球?  -这里不能玩\N- Just not ball games? - not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.90,0:47:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-告诉我数字游戏咋玩的  -我说过  那不是游戏\N- Tell me how the number game works. - I told you, it's not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.82,0:47:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都要有编号\NWe just all have numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.62,0:47:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙暮\NShmuel!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.68,0:48:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺!  你干什么去了\NBruno! what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.48,0:48:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球掉那边了  我刚把它拣回来\NMy ball went over. I was just getting it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.45,0:48:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这味道越烧越臭啦  是不?\NThey smell even worse when they burn, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.37,0:48:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.38,0:48:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吧...\NBut, surely you...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.90,0:49:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔莎  我发过誓要保密的\NElsa, I was sworn to secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.53,0:49:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-连自己老婆也不能说？  -是的\N- From your own wife. - yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.66,0:49:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以生命起誓  明白吗\NI took an oath upon my life. do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.92,0:49:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔莎  你也该和我一样\NElsa, you believe in this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.55,0:49:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-希望祖国强盛  -不不不  拉尔夫  不是那样\N- You want this country to be strong... - no, Ralf, no! no, not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.18,0:49:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎能...\NHow can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.72,0:49:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-因为我是军人  -你们怎能...\N- Because I'm a soldier. - how can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.43,0:49:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-军人为战争而战斗 -那不能算战争!\N- Soldiers fight wars. - that isn't war!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.27,0:49:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是战争的一部分  关键一环\NIt's a part of it! it's a vital part of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.48,0:49:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我以及大家心中的祖国\NThe fatherland we all desire, all of us, you included,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.57,0:49:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若我们不那么做  就不可能强盛\NCannot be achieved without work such as this!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.20,0:49:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-埃尔莎  -离我远点!  别碰我!\N- Elsa. Elsa. - get away from me! get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.75,0:49:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷来了\NGrandpa's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.17,0:50:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不敢相信  -爷爷来了\N- I don't believe this. - grandpa's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.30,0:50:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一会儿过去\NWe'll be through in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.40,0:50:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁跟你说的这事儿\NWho told you about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.26,0:50:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶怎么样\NHow's grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.35,0:50:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气变化她有点着凉了\NShe's a bit under the weather, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.89,0:50:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾  她等着盼着要见你们呢\NIt's a shame, she was so much looking forward to seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.06,0:51:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-下次吧  等她感觉好点  -一定\N- Perhaps next time, if she feels up to it. - absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.41,0:51:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子你要明白 你妈真是病了\NYou know, Ralf, your mother really is sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.00,0:51:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几周来她一直想着来着\NShe's been talking about this visit for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.50,0:51:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是被这想法吓出病来\NMaybe that's what's made her sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.88,0:51:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸跟我说你们有个家教老师\NSo, your father tells me that you've got a tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.72,0:51:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  他不错\NYes. he's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.35,0:51:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他不让我们读历险故事书\NBut he won't let us read any adventure books.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.60,0:51:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学的很没意思  全是古文历史\NAll we do is boring, old history.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.52,0:51:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说  小家伙\NLet me tell you something, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.73,0:51:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有过去的历史  我们今天无法围坐在一起\NIf it wasn't for history, we wouldn't all be sitting around this table.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.15,0:51:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸在这做的工作\NThe work your father is doing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.82,0:51:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是在创造历史\NHistory in the making.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.29,0:52:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像你这么大时  我最喜欢历史了\NWhen I was your age, history was my favourite subject by miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.26,0:52:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却很不合我爸的心意\NWhich obviously didn't please my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.63,0:52:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\NWhy not?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.05,0:52:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是一所大学里的文学教授\NWell, he was a professor of literature at the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.10,0:52:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  现在他还教课吗\NReally, does he still teach?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.44,0:52:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不是很清楚  -你这都不清楚\N- I don't really know. - you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.90,0:52:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很久没联系了\NWe're not in touch, my father and i.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.86,0:52:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他出国有段时间了\NHe left the country some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.16,0:52:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候\NReally, when?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.99,0:52:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年多了  指挥官\NAbout four years ago, Herr kommandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.84,0:52:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定还很年轻  大概四十出头\NBut surely he can't be very old. what is he, still in his 40s, late 40s?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.13,0:52:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去哪儿了\NWhere did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.77,0:53:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科勒特上尉\NLieutenant kotler,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.81,0:53:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那文学教授的父亲  去哪儿了\NYour father, the professor of literature, where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.20,0:53:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是瑞士吧  指挥官\NI believe it was Switzerland, Herr Kommandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.58,0:53:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎能选择离开自己的祖国\NHow strange that he should choose to leave the fatherland
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.04,0:53:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其在祖国最需要他\NAt the very moment it needed him most.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.62,0:53:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人人都该尽其所能的时刻\NJust when we're all required to play our part in the national revival.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.50,0:53:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒酒!\NMore wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.29,0:53:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他因为什么出国  他有结核之类的病吗\NWhat reason did he give? was he tubercular?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.01,0:53:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是去那儿疗养的吗\NDid he go there to take the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.22,0:53:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恐怕真不清楚  指挥官\NI'm afraid I really don't know, Herr Kommandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.10,0:53:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得问他自己\NYou'd have to ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.14,0:53:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那相当难吧  是不\NWell, that would be rather difficult, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.94,0:53:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他在瑞士\NWith him being in Switzerland.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.90,0:53:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点!\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.36,0:53:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨磨蹭蹭的老东西\NWhat's the matter with you tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.08,0:54:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就那原因  因为他病了\NYes, perhaps that was it. perhaps he was ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.79,0:54:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话  他就是反对祖国\NUnless, of course, he had disagreements.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.71,0:54:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我是说  不支持国家政策  -听说过这类人\N- I mean, with government policy. - one hears of such men.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.97,0:54:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们大多精神不好  或是胆小怕事\NDisturbed, most of them, or just plain cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.01,0:54:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不管怎样  他们都属于叛徒  -千真万确\N- Even so, all of them traitors. - absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.77,0:54:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你父亲是这种人的话\NPresumably, if that was the case with your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.10,0:54:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该遵守军人的职则  上报你的长官\NYou will have informed your superiors, as is your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.11,0:54:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科勒特上尉\NLieutenant Kotler!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.91,0:54:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹太垃圾  蠢猪\NYou cretin Jew! filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.84,0:54:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉尔夫\NRalf!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.97,0:54:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹太蠢猪!\NJew!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.22,0:55:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但是爸爸只是坐着  -你希望他做什么呢\N- But dad just sat there. - what did you expect him to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.14,0:55:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹太人活该\NThe Jew deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.99,0:55:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你一些农场的事  好吗\NCan I ask you something about the farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.99,0:55:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  你不是现在还认为那是个农场吧\NBruno, you don't still think it's a farm, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.68,0:55:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个营地  叫做劳作营\NIt's a camp. what's called a work camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.64,0:55:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然是给犹太人准备的\NFor Jews, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.69,0:55:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只给犹太人?\NJust Jews?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.35,0:55:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们干活儿最好吗\NBecause they're the best workers?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.27,0:55:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜  他们不是因为干的好才进去的\NThey're not in there because they're good, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.44,0:55:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们什么都干不好\NThey're no good at anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.28,0:55:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们邪恶才被关在里面\NThey're in there because they're evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.11,0:56:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他们是敌人  -敌人?\N- They're the enemy. - the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.37,0:56:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我以为和我们打仗的才是...-布鲁诺 他们很邪恶\N- But I thought we were fighting... - they're evil, Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.79,0:56:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶  危险的害人精\NEvil, dangerous vermin.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.37,0:56:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们让我们输掉战争的\NThey're the reason we lost the great war.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.21,0:56:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李斯特先生教我们的内容\NHaven't you been listening to anything
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.71,0:56:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都没听吗\NHerr Liszt has been telling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.25,0:56:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  基本没有\NNo. not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.63,0:56:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸应该不可怕吧  他是个好人\NDad's not horrible, is he? He's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.14,0:56:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-当然  -但是他管着那个可怕的地方\N- Of course, he is. - But he's in charge of a horrible place.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.89,0:56:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有对他们才是可怕的  布鲁诺\NIt's only horrible for them, Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.23,0:56:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该为爸爸感到无比骄傲\NWe should be proud of dad, now more than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.81,0:56:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正在让这个国家重新兴盛\NHe's making the country great again.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.62,0:57:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和你说的一样  他们有些奇怪  有些...\NLike you say, they're a bit strange. a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.91,0:57:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们和我们不一样\NWell, they're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.04,0:57:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是敌人  布鲁诺\NThey're the enemy, Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.00,0:57:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶  危险的害人精\NEvil, dangerous vermin.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.04,0:57:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不算是人\NWell, you see, they're not really people at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.36,0:58:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干什么\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.65,0:58:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们需要一个手小点的来清洗这些\NThey wanted someone with tiny fingers to clean all these.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.71,0:58:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不应该成为朋友\NWe're not supposed to be friends, you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.84,0:58:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们照理是敌人  你原来知道吗\NWe're meant to be enemies. did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.85,0:58:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃点吗\NDo you want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.03,0:58:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你的爸爸是个怎样的人  -怎么问他\N- What's your dad like? - What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.16,0:58:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个好人吗\NIs he a good man?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.70,0:58:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直认为他是个好人吗\NYou've never thought he wasn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.67,0:59:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为他自豪吗\NAnd you're proud of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.05,0:59:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不为你的爸爸骄傲吗\NAren't you proud of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.47,0:59:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在营里真的很可怕吗\NIs it really horrible in the camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.56,0:59:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么敢在屋里和人说话\NHow dare you talk to people in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.89,0:59:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么敢!\NHow dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.40,0:59:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吃东西吗\NAre you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.53,0:59:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在偷吃食物吗\NHave you been stealing food?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.53,0:59:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-回答我  -不  先生  他给我的\N- Answer me! - No, sir. he gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.83,0:59:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友\NHe's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.37,0:59:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.38,0:59:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小先生\NLittle man,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.59,0:59:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识这个犹太人吗\NDo you know this Jew?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.84,0:59:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识这个犹太人吗\NDo you know this Jew?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.34,0:59:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我正巧走进来  看到他在吃\NNo, I just walked in, and he was helping himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.89,0:59:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前从没见过他\NI've never seen him before in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.57,1:00:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把玻璃杯擦干净\NYou, finish cleaning the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.45,1:00:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来的时候再谈谈\NWhen I come back, we'll have a little chat
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.16,1:00:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何处置偷吃的老鼠  我们走\NAbout what happens to rats who steal. Come away.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.34,1:01:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新来到营里的会高兴地发现\NNew arrivals here are happy to discover that life in the camp
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.22,1:01:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营中的生活不仅仅是干活\NIs not all work.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.64,1:02:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多休闲时光\NAnd that there's ample opportunity for leisure also.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.81,1:02:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在铁炼厂干了一天的活\NAt the end of their day at the ironmongery
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.06,1:02:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者工地或鞋厂  工人们能享受\NOr the build or boot factory, the workers can enjoy
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.90,1:02:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营中提供的许多休闲娱乐项目\NThe many forms of pastime that the camp has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.15,1:02:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集体运动非常流行\NOrganised sport is very popular.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.95,1:02:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有玩的人也乐于观看\NThose that don't play certainly enjoy watching.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.12,1:02:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一天工作结束后\NAt the end of the working day,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.62,1:02:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中心咖啡吧是最棒的去处\NThe centrally located cafe is the ideal place
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.08,1:02:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友与家人在那里相聚\NFor friends and families to join
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.04,1:02:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享受美味营养的晚餐\NTogether for a hearty and nutritious meal.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.38,1:02:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其孩子们对酥饼和蛋糕爱不释手\NThe children, in particular, enjoy the pastries and cakes on offer.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.05,1:02:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上还时不时有音乐会\NIn the evenings, the occasional music concerts,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.64,1:02:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由访问乐团或者天才音乐者举办\NEither by visiting orchestras or, indeed, by talented musicians
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.77,1:02:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营里的人们都乐于观看\NFrom within the camp itself, are always well attended.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.90,1:02:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的娱乐项目包括图书馆\NOther recreations include reading in the library,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.36,1:02:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陶艺  料理  艺术  园艺  提供给所有人\NPottery, cookery, art and horticulture for adult and child alike.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.41,1:02:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营里的娱乐项目多\NAlmost any activity one could wish for
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.33,1:03:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就怕你想不到\NIs available within the camp.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.58,1:03:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错\NSplendid.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.01,1:03:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-精彩  了不起  -谢谢\N- Bravo. excellent. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.69,1:04:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  小小先生\NGoodbye, little man.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.23,1:04:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙暮  沙暮\NShmuel! shmuel!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.21,1:05:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.42,1:05:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了一个关于营里的影片\NI saw a film about the camp,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.26,1:05:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来真不错\NAnd it looked so nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.56,1:05:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我为什么会那么做\NI don't know why I did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.02,1:05:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷特尔和每个人都那么说\NGretel and everyone were saying all these things,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.86,1:05:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个士兵很吓人\NAnd that soldier's so scary.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.32,1:05:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来过好几天你都不在\NBeen coming here for days, but you were never here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.03,1:05:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为我们不再是朋友了\NI thought maybe we weren't friends any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.26,1:06:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙暮  我为我的行为道歉\NShmuel, I'm really sorry for what I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.38,1:06:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们仍是朋友吧\NWe are still friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.25,1:06:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科特这些天到哪去了  我好久没见他了\NWhere's Kurt these days? I haven't seen him for ages.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.21,1:06:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谁是科特  -科勒特中尉\N- Who's Kurt? - Lieutenant Kotler.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.68,1:06:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被调去前线\NHe's been moved to the front.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.10,1:06:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的青春与热情\NIt was felt that his youth and enthusiasm
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.14,1:06:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在那里得到最大发挥\NWould be put to better use there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.89,1:06:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥官  您的电话\NHerr Kommandant, telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.94,1:06:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上  格雷特尔  他会调去那里\NIn actual fact, Gretel, he was sent there
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.48,1:07:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为他没有通告上级\NBecause he failed to inform the authorities
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.36,1:07:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的父亲对党不忠\NOf his father's lack of loyalty to the party.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.82,1:07:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须指出  那是他的义务\NWhich was his duty, I might add.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.74,1:07:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是他运气坏  -运气坏?\N- Which was his bad luck. - Bad luck?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.91,1:07:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不走运的是他父亲不忠\NWell, bad luck that it was his father who was disloyal,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.87,1:07:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是母亲\NAnd not his mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.08,1:07:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般认为没有必要通报母亲不忠\NOne presumably doesn't have to report one's mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.34,1:07:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么?  -帕维尔什么时候回来\N- What? - When will Pavel be back?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.47,1:07:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-妈妈  -永远不会回来  傻瓜\N- Mum? - Never, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.89,1:07:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父亲的来电  他们遭到轰炸\NIt's father. They've been bombed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.73,1:07:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶死了\NGrandmother's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.99,1:08:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为我们和那些死去的人\N"...The victory which you have obtained for us
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.49,1:08:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所取得的胜利\N"And for all who sleep in him,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.87,1:08:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生者永远铭记\N"Keep us who are still in the body in everlasting fellowship
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.54,1:08:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世间的等待\N"With all that wait for thee on earth,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.91,1:08:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了天国的重逢\N"And with all that are around thee in heaven,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.42,1:08:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了与神子耶稣的相会\N"In union with him who is the resurrection
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.84,1:08:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣灵与你同生  伴你复活\N"And the life, who live and reigneth with thee and the holy ghost,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.63,1:08:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的神  无尽的世界  阿门（纳粹的标志）\N"Ever one god, world without end. Amen."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.76,1:08:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不可以在上面  她不会想要的\NHe can't have that on there. she wouldn't have wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.56,1:08:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想要\NHe does.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.04,1:09:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万能的神  以自身之死...\N"Almighty god, who by the death of..."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.42,1:09:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有去过葬礼\NHave you ever been to a funeral?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.71,1:09:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来这以后马上祖父母都死了\NMy grandma and grandpa both died just after we got here,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.22,1:09:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有葬礼\NBut there weren't any funerals.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.93,1:09:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个从那里走到那里\NThat one there to there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.31,1:09:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们同时死的吗\NThey both died at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.15,1:09:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么死的\NWhat of?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.90,1:09:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.07,1:09:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸说他们定是来这途中感染得病\NPapa said they must have caught something on the way here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.99,1:09:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一到这里他们就去了医院\NThey had to go to a hospital as soon as we arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.24,1:09:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们再也没有见过他们\NWe didn't see them again.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.42,1:10:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很好玩\NThis is fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.13,1:10:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我们能玩些更好玩的\NWish we could do something a bit more exciting, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.68,1:10:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那个从那走到那  -这个吗\N- That one there to there. - This one?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.97,1:10:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是这个吗  -不  那个\N- This one? - No, that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.43,1:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这个走到这吗  -不  走到那里\N- This one to here? - No, there!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.64,1:10:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-走到这里吗  -不\N- To here? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.77,1:10:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这里吗  -不\N- Here? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.24,1:10:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我希望你一直在这  -我也想\N- I don't want you to go away again. - No. neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.86,1:11:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可以这样\NYou can't behave like this!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.57,1:11:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你在对我的行为质问吗  -不能再这样\N- You're questioning my behaviour? - It can't continue!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.15,1:11:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  我不能再忍了  拉尔夫\NI know. I can't stand this any more, Ralf.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.70,1:11:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能在这  与这有关系\NI can't stay here and be a part of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.54,1:11:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不认为会有问题吗\NDon't you think there will be questions?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.33,1:11:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-问题?  -大家会议论\N- Questions? - Well, now, what does it say
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.83,1:11:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连家都管理不好\NAbout my ability to carry out my work
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.79,1:11:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做好工作\NIf I cannot control my own family?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.59,1:11:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-工作?  你叫这工作?  -冷静点  女人\N- Work? Is that what you call it? - Pull yourself together, woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.59,1:11:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就忽略它  当没看到\NRight. Just ignore it. Ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.42,1:11:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忽略这个事实  我嫁了个恶魔\NIgnore the fact that the man I married is a monster!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.51,1:11:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连你的母亲也不会爱你\NEven your own mother couldn't love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.90,1:11:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里快乐吗\NAre you happy here?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.07,1:11:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  很快乐\NYes. very.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.03,1:12:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢  格雷特尔\NAnd you, Gretel?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.45,1:12:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原来是的  不过现在想家  想朋友\NWell, I was, but I do miss home. I miss my friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.67,1:12:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  当然  你肯定也是  布鲁诺\NYes, I'm sure. And you, too, Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.63,1:12:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定想你的朋友\NYou must miss those friends of yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.63,1:12:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一点不想了  真的\NNo. not any more, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.10,1:12:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的问题是  如果有机会\NI suppose the real question is, if the opportunity arose,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.99,1:12:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会想离开去别处住吗\NWould you prefer to live somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.40,1:12:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-回家吗  -不  不是回柏林  还不是时候\N- Back home? - No. Not Berlin. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.83,1:12:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去安全的地方  像海德堡罗蒂阿姨的家\NSomewhere safe, say aunt Lottie's in Heidelberg, for example.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.17,1:12:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们全家  你也一块吗\NAll of us? you as well?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.50,1:12:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  目前恐怕不行\NNo. That won't be possible just yet, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.84,1:12:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须留在这里完成工作\NI must stay and complete my work here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.89,1:13:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前  你们的母亲觉得\NSee, at the moment, your mother is finding it...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.77,1:13:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她认为你们应该去别处生活\NShe just feels right now you need to spend some time elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.06,1:13:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们喜欢吗\NWould you like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.87,1:13:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺  生活\NI'm afraid, Bruno, in life,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.78,1:13:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常让人身不由己\NWe often have to do things we don't want to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.45,1:13:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的事你们母亲觉得这里\NThe important thing is your mother does not feel
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.21,1:13:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不适合你们\NThat this is an appropriate place for you
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.08,1:13:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡过童年生活\NTo be spending your childhood,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.17,1:13:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多想想\NAnd the more I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.59,1:13:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她确实说的对\NThe more I realise she's very probably right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.88,1:13:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但是  爸爸...  -不\N- But, Dad... - No!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.47,1:13:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候你们搬走了\NIt's time for you to move away.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.92,1:14:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧\NIs everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.88,1:14:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们找不到爸爸\NWe can't find papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.84,1:14:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和一些别的人去了别的工地\NHe went on a different work duty with some of the men,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.55,1:14:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没有回来\NAnd they haven't come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.77,1:14:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有些坏消息  我要离开了\NI've got some bad news, too. I'm going away.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.23,1:14:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次离开多久呢\NHow long for this time?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.65,1:14:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说是坏消息  可能是永远\NThat's why it's bad. It's forever, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.24,1:14:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说这里不适合孩子  真是愚蠢\NMum says this is no place for children, which is just stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.08,1:14:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你什么时候走呢  -明天  午饭后\N- When do you go? - Tomorrow. after lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.38,1:15:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我以后再也见不到你了吗\NSo, I won't ever see you again?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.05,1:15:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以见到我  假期如果喜欢可以来柏林\NYes, you will. You can come on holiday to berlin if you like,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.22,1:15:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等大家都和睦相处的时候\NWhen everybody's getting on with each other again.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.27,1:15:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能帮你找到你的爸爸\NI wish I could've helped you find your dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.77,1:15:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的希望能做些弥补\NI really want to make up for letting you down like I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.32,1:15:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样真的能弥补  是吧  帮你找到爸爸\NThat would have done it, wouldn't it? Helping you find your dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.40,1:15:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很棒  就像一个机密任务\NWould've been great. Like a secret mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.12,1:15:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我可以从下面挖开  -什么  用那个吗\N- I could dig under. - What? With that?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.54,1:15:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  但我能带工具\NNo, but I could bring something.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.54,1:15:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边可一点都不好玩\NYou don't want to come over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.30,1:15:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.97,1:15:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我能去你那边  -干什么呢\N- I could come through to your side. - what's the point in that?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.35,1:15:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸肯定不会在我这边  是吧\NYour dad's not going to be over here, is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.81,1:16:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我过来肯定会显眼  是吧\NBut I'd stick out though, wouldn't I, if I came through?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.86,1:16:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你们不一样\NI don't look like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.49,1:16:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打扮一下\NYou could look like me, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.66,1:16:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿成一样的衣服  剃了头发\NIf you dressed like me and shaved your hair off.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.08,1:16:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会把头发剃了\NI'm not shaving my hair off.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.50,1:16:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你可以戴帽子  -我的睡衣颜色不对\N- You could cover it with a cap. - My pyjamas are a different colour.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.75,1:16:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以带给你  那里有一房的睡衣\NI could bring some. there's a hut full of them,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.59,1:16:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几千件  你真的愿意吗\NThousands of them. Would you do it, though?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.30,1:16:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我想那么做  -你真的敢吗\N- I want to do it. - Would you dare do it, though?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.59,1:16:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我想帮你找到你爸爸  -我得走了\N- I want to help you find your dad. - I've got to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.26,1:16:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就明天  我会带超大三明治\NTomorrow, then? I'll bring an extra-big sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.72,1:16:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了睡衣\NAnd don't forget the pyjamas!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.91,1:17:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺\NBruno?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.83,1:17:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  我能去荡秋千吗\NMum, can I go and play on the swing?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.05,1:17:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-布鲁诺  -最后一次了\N- Bruno... - It's my last chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.22,1:17:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那去吧\NAll right. go on then.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.13,1:18:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你不来了\NI thought you weren't coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.59,1:18:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  不容易脱身\NI'm sorry. it wasn't easy to get away.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.46,1:18:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天不容易出门  你忘了睡衣\NI'm not meant to be out here today. You forgot the pyjamas!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.97,1:18:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-三明治带了吗  -我怎么会让你失望\N- Did you bring the sandwich? - Would I let you down?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.08,1:19:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙暮\NShmuel.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.05,1:19:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.98,1:19:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看起来如何\NHow do I look?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.87,1:19:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  让我们开始干活\NRight. let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.05,1:19:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺\NBruno?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.60,1:20:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点深够了\NThat's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.38,1:20:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去找你爸爸\NLet's go and find your dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.89,1:20:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点!\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.76,1:20:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺小主人\NMaster Bruno?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.97,1:21:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙暮\NShmuel.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.48,1:21:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-能去咖啡吧或者别的地方吗  -咖啡吧?\N- Can we go to the cafe or something? - cafe?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.48,1:21:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-也许我该回家了  -那爸爸呢\N- Maybe I should go home. - What about papa?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.83,1:21:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先查下我们的屋子\NWe'll check our hut first.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.09,1:22:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺\NBruno?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.68,1:22:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.24,1:22:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸?\NPapa?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.66,1:22:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来! 起来!\NUp! up! get up!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.99,1:22:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-发生什么事了  -我不知道\N- What's happening? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.08,1:22:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有时会走队列\NWe go on marches sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.96,1:22:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走!  起来!\NMove! up, up!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.13,1:22:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走! 走!\NMove, move!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.60,1:22:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺\NBruno!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.23,1:22:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定还在外面  夫人\NHe must still be outside somewhere, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.37,1:23:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺\NBruno!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.62,1:23:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺\NBruno?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.64,1:23:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-走!  -快点!\N- Move! - Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.52,1:23:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来!\NGet up!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.31,1:23:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来  你必须起来!\NGet up. you must!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.44,1:23:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们拖出来!\NMove them out!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.45,1:23:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...那样我们每周的容纳人数\N...which means that our weekly capabilities
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.79,1:23:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会几乎翻三翻\NWould be almost tripled,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.41,1:23:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样  在夏天结束之前\NSo, therefore, by the end of the summer...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.75,1:23:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-拉尔夫  -埃尔莎  我在开会\N- Ralf. - Elsa, I'm in a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.46,1:24:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺不见了\NBruno's missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.80,1:24:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点!\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.81,1:24:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里等着!\NWait here!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.32,1:24:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点!\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.54,1:24:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走!  快走!\NMove! move!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.88,1:24:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到队伍里去!\NJoin the queue!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.68,1:24:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  你\NCome on, you!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.27,1:25:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺\NBruno!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.82,1:25:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\NMove it!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.03,1:25:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续\NGo on.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.99,1:25:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺\NBruno!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.00,1:25:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我们就在这里等雨停\NIt's all right. I think we're just waiting in here until the rain stops.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.97,1:25:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱下衣服!\NClothes off!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.52,1:25:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去哪里\NWhere are we going?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.07,1:25:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个淋浴\NNo, it's just a shower.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.69,1:25:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淋浴?\NA shower?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.99,1:26:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门!  开门!\NOpen the gates! open the gates!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.33,1:26:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走!\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.50,1:28:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺\NBruno!
